io.craigmiller160.school.entity

Class ScJoinHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.craigmiller160.school.entity.ScJoinHolder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JoinHolder, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ScJoinHolder>

    @Entity(name="student_course")
public class ScJoinHolder
extends java.lang.Object
implements JoinHolder, java.lang.Comparable<ScJoinHolder>, java.io.Serializable
    A representation of the join table in the database joining Student and Course entities. It is used to get lists of either or both entities via the join between them.

    THREAD SAFETY: This class is NOT thread-safe. Its state is not synchronized, and instances of it should be handled in a way that is not shared between threads.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    craig
